+# BA Compliance Re-Scan Retro — 2026-03-31 (Heartbeat 2)
+
+## Context
+
+BES-8 was marked done by Engineer. Re-scanned to verify fixes were applied correctly.
+
+## Work Done
+
+- Re-scanned messages/de.json + messages/tr.json for forbidden wording
+- Discovered BES-8 was only partially fixed
+- Created BES-12 (critical) with 2 new critical violations + 4 missed keys
+
+## Findings
+
+### What Was Fixed Correctly in BES-8 ✓
+- `profitierst du` (3 instances) → replaced with benefit/fee language
+- `Mögliche Gewinne` → `Mögliche Belohnungen`
+- `Besitzer-Bonus` → `Halter-Bonus`
+- `dpcOwnership` key (2x DE + 2x TR) → fixed
+- `dpcTooltip` Spieleranteil → fixed
+- `Credits-Preisgelder` → `Credits-Preise`
+- TradingDisclaimer on Airdrop (BES-9) ✓
+
+### What Was Missed / New Violations in BES-12
+1. `de.json:3358` — "dein Anteil an einem Spieler" → Spieleranteil (CRITICAL, not in BES-8!)
+2. `de.json:4357` — "Dein Anteil an einem Fussballspieler" → Spieleranteil (CRITICAL, not in BES-8!)
+3. `de.json:3901` — `dpcOwned: "Scout Card Besitz"` → engineer fixed `dpcOwnership` not `dpcOwned`
+4. `de.json:4060` — `inPossession: "{count} im Besitz"` → different key, missed
+5. `tr.json:3901` — `dpcOwned: "Scout Card Sahipliği"` → missed
+6. `tr.json:4060` — `inPossession: "{count} sahipliğinde"` → missed
+7. Multiple `Besitzer` (holder) uses → borderline, recommend `Halter`
+
+## Lessons
+
+### Root Cause of Partial Fix
+Engineer searched for the exact key names from BES-8 (`dpcOwnership`), not the semantic content. Multiple keys with the same forbidden content were missed because they had different names.
+
+### Rule Promotion
+**For future compliance audits: scan by CONTENT (grep forbidden words), not by key name.** The BES-8 approach was content-based (grep) — but the fix verification should also be content-based. If BES-8 had been re-scanned after the fix, the 4 missed keys would have been caught.
+
+### New Pattern Found
+"Anteil an einem Spieler/Fußballspieler" = explicit Spieleranteil language. This exact phrase should be added to the grep pattern list alongside "profitierst", "Besitz", "Sahipliği".
